-- Gold Futures Rise 0.4% on Comex in New York, Erasing Earlier Loss of 0.9%
-- Steve Stroth
-- 2010-07-22T13:52:34Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-07-22/gold-futures-rise-0-4-on-comex-in-new-york-erasing-earlier-loss-of-0-9-.html

          
          
             Gold futures for August delivery
rose $5, or 0.4 percent, to $1,196.80 an ounce at 9:52 a.m. on
the Comex in New York. Earlier, the price fell as much as 0.9
percent.  
          
          


  


        